All e-mail posts made by members of our  
Yahoo Group are the copyrighted work being infringed on.

Our home page states not to copy without permission.  At the end of each  
member's post there is also a note: "Reposting of any messages or  
information in this group is prohibited without permission of group owner"

Our member's posts are without permission being automatically posted as we
 
write them to intervertebraldiscdisease.blogspot.com/*

There is no contact information on the Blog, so we have no way to contact 

this mystery Blogger to ask this to stop.  All we can find is the Blog ID 

from the source code:  blogID=3064544769475329643.
